Rating: 3
A delicious cake. The batter is tasty and tender and the plums work like a charm - the plums I had were very sour but after being baked on top of the cake they turned out great. I used a 20cm (8in) round cake pan with a removable bottom and lined the base of the pan with a circle of baking paper. It worked really well.

